title: #92Noon! Wilcots/Larson/Props/Greenway/JonK
description: Solomon Wilcots joins us from Atlanta on radio row for the SB, St Cloud Huskies HC Brett Larson makes his 92noon debut, Wild winger Jordan Greenway calls in before team returns to practice and Jon Krawczynski in studio to wrap show. Some SB prop bet fodder in the mix as well!
